Search for the file inviteapi.min.js in the activation page

Then you use the command line to make a code with makeInviteCode()

Decrypt the ROT13:

From : Va beqre gb trarengr gur vaivgr pbqr, znxr n CBFG erdhrfg gb /ncv/vaivgr/trarengr
To: In order to generate the invite code, make a POST request to /api/invite/generate

Terminal and use:

curl -XPOST https://www.hackthebox.eu/api/invite/generate

{"success":1,"data":{"code":"QlNJRkgtT0lGVkwtUEFaWVYtUkdKWkUtTUdLQVY=","format":"encoded"},"0":200}

